<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN"<HTML lang="ja"><html><head><title>Particle Quiz</title><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"></head><script LANGUAGE="javascript" type="text/JavaScript">		var numQuestions = 9;		var numAnswered = 0;		var numCorrect = 0;		var q_id=245;</script>		<SCRIPT LANGUAGE="JavaScript" SRC="../../../../js/quiz_top.js"></SCRIPT><LINK href="../../../../css/particleQuiz.css" type=text/css rel=stylesheet><body class="backgroundColor"><h2 class="titleText" align="center"> 助詞クイズ </h2><div class="backgroundLayer" align="center" id="quiz"><div class="innerTitle"> Exemplification: Particles 〜に、〜な</div><div class="quizlistLine" ><a href="../../../../gquiz.php">Return    to Practice Quizzes list page</span></a></div>		<p class="instructionLine"> 正しいじょし(particle)をえらびなさい。</p><FORM name="quiz">	<! Question 1>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>1. </b>ミキはねこみたい	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('3',this.value,0)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>に</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>な</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>X</OPTION>	</SELECT>ですね。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>	<! Question 2>	<div class="questionLineEven"><b>2. </b>これはりんごのよう 	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('1',this.value,1)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>に</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>な</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>X</OPTION>    </SELECT>あかいです。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>		<! Question 3>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>3. </b>あのいぬは、うしのよう	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('1',this.value,2)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>に</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>な</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>X</OPTION>	</SELECT>歩きます。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>		<! Question 4>	<div class="questionLineEven"><b>4. </b>うしのよう	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('2',this.value,3)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>に</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>な</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>X</OPTION>	</SELECT>顔です。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>		<! Question ５>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>5. </b>このりんごはハニーみたい	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('1',this.value,4)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>に</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>な</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>X</OPTION>	</SELECT>あまいよ。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>		<! Question 6>	<div class="questionLineEven"><b>6. </b>あの人の顔はフットボールのよう	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('3',this.value,5)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>に</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>な</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>X</OPTION>	</SELECT>です。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>		<! Question 7>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>7. </b>あの人はねこのよう	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('3',this.value,6)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>に</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>な</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>X</OPTION>	</SELECT>です。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>		<! Question 8>	<div class="questionLineEven"><b>8. </b>あの人はねこのよう	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('1',this.value,7)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>に</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>な</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>X</OPTION>	</SELECT>ねます。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>		<! Question 9>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>9. </b>あの人はねこのよう	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('2',this.value,8)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>に</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>な</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>X</OPTION>	</SELECT>人です。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>					</FORM><div id="score"></div><div><table class="optionBox"><tr>	<td><BUTTON onClick="checkAnswers()">Check Answers</BUTTON></td>	<td><BUTTON onClick="resetValues()">Reset Values</BUTTON></td></tr></table></div></div></body></html>